[whines]

268
00:15:05,729 --> 00:15:08,523
[RUDEUS]
Gah, what a bunch of hotheads.

269
00:15:23,580 --> 00:15:24,748
[GINGER]
Pardon me!

270
00:15:30,545 --> 00:15:31,671
[RUDEUS]
Comin'!

271
00:15:35,342 --> 00:15:37,761
[GINGER]
