everything else is settled.

291
00:16:21,888 --> 00:16:23,473
[RUIJERD] Are you sure
you're fine by yourself?

292
00:16:23,556 --> 00:16:25,308
Oh please, you know me.

293
00:16:25,392 --> 00:16:27,894
First sign of trouble,
I'll fly right back to you two.

294
00:16:27,977 --> 00:16:29,688
Will you look after Aisha?

295
00:16:29,771 --> 00:16:30,897
Yeah, you got it!

296
00:16:30,980 --> 00:16:33,358
