298
00:16:49,040 --> 00:16:50,917
[gasps]

299
00:16:52,752 --> 00:16:55,630
[RUDEUS] So this is
where she's been living.

300
00:16:56,798 --> 00:16:58,341
[GINGER]
Lady Roxy has told us all about

301
00:16:58,425 --> 00:17:00,677
your knack for
silent spellcasting.

302
00:17:00,760 --> 00:17:03,596
I'm honored to finally
meet her genius student.

303
00:17:03,680 --> 00:17:05,765
[RUDEUS]
She called me a genius?

304
00:17:05,849 --> 00:17:08,768
She boasts about you quite
often, as a matter of fact.

305
00:17:08,852 --> 00:17:10,478
She said she felt
she wasn't qualified

306
00:17:10,562 --> 00:17:12,772
to teach someone
of your caliber.

307
00:17:12,856 --> 00:17:16,568
