an exaggeration.

308
00:17:18,820 --> 00:17:19,821
[GINGER]
This way, please.

309
00:17:19,904 --> 00:17:21,031
Huh?

310
00:17:24,034 --> 00:17:25,410
Okay.

311
00:17:37,797 --> 00:17:40,050
[SOLDIERS] Thank you for
your dedicated service.

312
00:17:40,133 --> 00:17:41,843
[RUDEUS]
Wait a sec.

313
00:17:41,926 --> 00:17:44,054
You're the two guys
from yesterday, right?

314
00:17:44,137 --> 00:17:46,723
[GINGER] Excuse me.
May I take your staff and bags?

315
00:17:46,806 --> 00:17:49,017
Oh, yeah, thanks.

316
00:17:52,228 --> 00:17:55,398
[RUDEUS] Eh, whatever.
I should focus on Roxy for now.

317
00:17:55,482 --> 00:17:58,151
I mean, I haven't
seen her in seven years!

318
00:17:58,234 --> 00:18:00,195
I have so much to tell her!

319
00:18:00,278 --> 00:18:02,947
[GINGER]
Lord Rudeus. Um.

320
00:18:03,031 --> 00:18:04,240
[RUDEUS]
Yes?

321
00:18:05,909 --> 00:18:08,036
[GINGER]
Never mind. It's nothing.

322
00:18:11,122 --> 00:18:12,248
[GINGER]
This is Ginger!

323
00:18:12,332 --> 00:18:14,918
I have brought the young
Lord Rudeus with me!

324
00:18:15,001 --> 00:18:16,795
[PAX]
Enter!

325
00:18:16,878 --> 00:18:20,590
[RUDEUS]
