331
00:18:52,038 --> 00:18:53,873
[PAX]
Drop him, boys!

332
00:19:05,885 --> 00:19:08,054
Ah, jeez. What the hell?

333
00:19:08,138 --> 00:19:10,390
Not exactly a warm welcome.

334
00:19:33,246 --> 00:19:35,874
[PAX laughs]
It's futile!

335
00:19:35,957 --> 00:19:38,084
That magic circle is
a King-class barrier

336
00:19:38,168 --> 00:19:40,879
I had created
specifically to trap Roxy!

337
00:19:40,962 --> 00:19:43,965
A child like you has
no hope of breaking free!

338
00:19:44,049 --> 00:19:45,592
And you would be?

339
00:19:45,675 --> 00:19:47,385
I thought you'd never ask.

340
00:19:47,469 --> 00:19:49,179
I'm Pax, seventh
prince of Shirone,

341
00:19:49,262 --> 00:19:51,431
and your worst nightmare!

342
00:19:52,182 --> 00:19:55,185
