please call Roxy here.

346
00:20:02,025 --> 00:20:03,151
I'm her former student
and she can confirm--

347
00:20:03,234 --> 00:20:05,111
[PAX]
Roxy isn't here.

348
00:20:05,195 --> 00:20:06,363
Huh?

349
00:20:06,446 --> 00:20:08,198
[PAX]
Roxy isn't here!

350
00:20:08,281 --> 00:20:11,993
