in my domain!

354
00:20:16,956 --> 00:20:20,168
W-Wait, you think I'm her lover?

355
00:20:20,251 --> 00:20:21,461
Aren't you?

356
00:20:21,544 --> 00:20:22,962
[RUDEUS]
Oh, thank god.

357
00:20:23,046 --> 00:20:24,005
Sounds like I haven't been

358
00:20:24,089 --> 00:20:26,257
cucked by this
little creep after all.

359
00:20:26,341 --> 00:20:27,550
That's something, at least.

360
00:20:27,634 --> 00:20:30,470
Perish the thought, sir,
that's incomprehensible!

361
00:20:30,553 --> 00:20:34,516
I am but her humble and
utterly unworthy apprentice!

362
00:20:35,725 --> 00:20:37,060
Well, good enough!

363
00:20:37,143 --> 00:20:39,396
Roxy never did shut up
about her precious student,

364
00:20:39,479 --> 00:20:41,731
